Steps to Manage Delta Lake History


Set Retention Duration:
--------------------------------
spark.conf.set("spark.databricks.delta.retentionDurationCheck.enabled", "false")
spark.conf.set("spark.databricks.delta.logRetentionDuration", "interval 1 days")
spark.conf.set("spark.databricks.delta.deletedFileRetentionDuration", "interval 1 days")


Disabling Retention Duration Check:
-----------------------------
spark.conf.set("spark.databricks.delta.retentionDurationCheck.enabled", "false")
